{"tid":351141,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔獸爭霸]Warmane 80級私服","createTime":"2017-08-07T18:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T21:43:15.000Z","uid":73938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c28304db578b290aad1900a638fc85daa421d0a6","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:16:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">魔獸世界係一個RPG角色扮演嘅遊戲，入面分別有兩個陣型，分別係聯盟同部落，咁而我地玩緊嘅80級遊戲版本就係有分戰士、聖騎、死騎、術士、法師、薩滿、德魯伊、牧師、獵人、盜賊。遊戲玩法分PVP同PVE，適合唔同嘅遊戲玩家。PVP就可以係野外地圖打野戰、打戰場、打競技場，而PVE就係瘋狂打副本，解成就之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n正題：<br />\nWarmane 80級私服已經開左7年，伺服器十分穩定，唔需要擔心自己努力升裝升等級升好耐係一日之內冇曬，同時間我地80級私服比起其他私服已經修復好多bug，成就最高可達一萬成就點以上，任務都極少有Bug。所以基本上差不多係還原官服，而且伺服器人數每日高達1.5K人數以上，因伺服器得1.2K位，而伺服器又設在歐洲，所以每日八點後上線就需要排隊，而唔想排隊就需要比90港紙就可以永久免排隊。<br />\n<br />\n而係今日我地係之前LIHKG開過post招人，現在加入嘅巴打最勁嘅已經組左一團10人ICC啦，其他巴打就已經組織左一個10人ICC新手團供新巴打加入。總共活躍人數已經有20個左右，歡迎更加多巴絲們加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/334079255170252810/344174833745264640/2.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F334079255170252810%2F344174833745264640%2F2.PNG&h=715cccc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/334079255170252810/344174852753719296/3.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F334079255170252810%2F344174852753719296%2F3.PNG&h=eeea017e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOK<br />\n想加入的話 首先請下載 Discord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://discordapp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordapp.com%2F&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cabf6769\" target=\"_blank\">https://discordapp.com/</a><br />\nGroup Link: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/8ZPESAP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F8ZPESAP&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=303feda0\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/8ZPESAP</a><br />\n<br />\n其次上遊戲官網註冊帳號<br />\nLink: <a href=\"http://www.warmane.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.warmane.com&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=117e88d1\" target=\"_blank\">www.warmane.com</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲下載地址<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE%2Fview&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fa1f06ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view</a><br />\n<br />\n註冊完 下載完仲差幾步就玩得<br />\n首先解壓-&gt;再去主目錄搵Data嘅File -&gt; 搵zhTW嘅File -&gt; 用txt檔開realmlist-&gt;改做SET realmlist &quot;<a href=\"http://logon.warmane.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flogon.warmane.com&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=407d672b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">logon.warmane.com</a>&quot; <br />\n<br />\n跟住去返主目錄 開Game再Login 選擇Icecrown 伺服器就玩得<br />\n<br />\n如果入game有顯示咩你所登錄語音同伺服器唔同<br />\n請下載下面Bat檔放入主目錄 開啟<br />\n開左Bat就係開game 之後就應該冇事<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f870dcb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手加入會比G比包包等升級個時唔驚冇錢學技又冇包包 位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"33334a86598d2c7700864e886e3860383420c562","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"對唔住各位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n標題係魔獸世界 唔係魔獸爭霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9957b2e9e3b520b1db25d68019812464c1c798","tid":351141,"uid":70830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:32:35.000Z","msg":"有冇話咩CPU/幾多RAM先玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075ac19bbe1acbad3172a20b417adfa756eb40d7","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇話咩CPU/幾多RAM先玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好久嘅機都玩到"},{"pid":"0c23b08dd5e6a3a6847479de273694e99cfb8bc1","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:51:39.000Z","msg":"更正 sever係有15K人上線 一萬五千<br />\n<br />\n平時係game打gs用慣 sor"},{"pid":"4afb5d93a9cecb4cab39f672d5a2667853a5beee","tid":351141,"uid":15156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963c12bfcb75bd488f95a40512e57a67db2a78a8","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6f1d0cf0ffae60d8a5eb61a2a44b686f069eb43","tid":351141,"uid":15156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9528ddc3a19e16bc3ce49f8aec7d029dfadcb81","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e13ade32ae074153b62e1abd1df4c3b5ca5045e","tid":351141,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:34:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"679e0f2ee7e9c0d642fa